  abstract =     "In spite of a worldwide trend towards the use of
                  outline fonts for displays and for printing devices,
                  they are still not very common in the east Asian
                  countries where Chinese characters are used. The
                  reason for this is that the complex, structured
                  shapes of Chinese characters take a long time to
                  design and develop.

